Apache sqoop
How to validate all the service available are running in VM.
ps -ef|grep -i manager

and look for ResourceManager & Node manager (yarn and map reduce ) also look for Node
ps -ef|grep -i node [and look for datanode, secondarynode]

you can also run 
ps -fu hdfs 

ps -fu yarn

mysql -u retail_dba -p [password cloudera]
user retail_db;
show tables;

